root: ^(This one is very beautiful and is basically a luxury home anyone would love)
^(After looking around this one does hit a lot of the checkboxes)
^(There is an in-ground pool installed as well as a home theater)
^(There is also an in-law suite, something that the other house was lacking)
^(Good area with very good schools around here)
^(There is a basketball court too, man it would be awesome to live here)
^(It is equally as distant to David's work as the other home, so that cancels out)
^(It is quite a bit above budget with a listing of $2.9M)
^(I know David and Sarah do have wealthy parents so it is worth a shot)
